media.ext_alt_text: White-on-blue cross stitch showing line art of the full lunar lander, plus part of the command module attached to it. There’s also a black iPhone sitting off to one side, covering the other stitches.

text:
iPhone: “I’m more powerful than the computers that put man on the Moon!”

Apollo Guidance Computer: “So you keep saying, but remind me—of the two of us, who has actually put a man on the Moon?”
